SEC. 4.

Specific Powers.

âThe PHILCORIN is authorized and directed:

To establish or help establish, maintain, and operate one central research center and such other research centers and sub-stations in any part of the Philippines as may be deemed necessary;

To procure materials, supplies, and equipment as may be necessary to prosecute successfully its researches and experimental works;

To conduct scientific and technological seminars, conventions and conferences of coconut researches or send delegates and observers to such conferences and conventions ;

To solicit, receive and award grants, bequests and donations given for the purpose of aiding scientific and technological research and investigation on coconut to government and private institutions; and

To secure patent rights to its inventions and discoveries and to exploit the same.
